Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:54.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気のふちを行くゲーム Ｅカード
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.56,default,,0,0,0,,E-Card, a game heading\Ntowards an abyss of insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.68,default,,0,0,0,,A big bet was placed just before\Nthe final round.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:58.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その最終戦を前にした大勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持たざる者 カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:03.54,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji finally makes his move\Nagainst the old fox, Tonegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:04.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに 老かい利根川を討つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:08.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:08.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血の代償と引き換えに得る大金
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:10.84,default,,0,0,0,,He gives his blood in exchange\Nfor a huge sum of 11.1 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:12.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1110万円
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は決したかに見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:14.86,default,,0,0,0,,It seemed that the battle\Nwas finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.52,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji had an intuitive flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし カイジを貫く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある ひらめき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.29,default,,0,0,0,,I can win the 12th round too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:23.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる 12戦目も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:25.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 18ミリだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:25.26,default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet 18 mm\Nin another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:32.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 生き死にの ばくち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:30.70,default,,0,0,0,,One more life-or-death gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.39,default,,0,0,0,,The insanity is not yet over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:35.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気の沙汰は まだ終わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.35,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Heart's Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何言いだすんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.70,default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you trying to do,\NKaiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の勝ちだって奇跡的なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.30,default,,0,0,0,,It was already a miracle\Nfor you to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:49.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう十分じゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:49.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう次は ないっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:47.99,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:49.78,default,,0,0,0,,There won't be a next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:51.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほっとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.32,default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:53.13,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ち運に乗ってるここで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下がれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:56.47,default,,0,0,0,,I can't back down when\Nluck is on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.53,default,,0,0,0,,When will I ever\Nget such a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今行かずに どうするんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むちゃですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.05,default,,0,0,0,,Don't be reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.48,default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, just get me a towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それより タオルだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タオルをもう１本 持ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.14,default,,0,0,0,,Bring me another towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.54,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:11.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早くしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.27,default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:12.57,default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:14.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この ばかが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:18.90,default,,0,0,0,,This idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.62,default,,0,0,0,,He's getting too full\Nof himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,調子に乗りおって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き死にの ばくちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.52,default,,0,0,0,,What's with another\Nlife-or-death gamble?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:36.03,default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful...\NThis is wonderful, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:34.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:36.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実に すばらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:39.12,default,,0,0,0,,You only have one life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命は １つしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:43.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから大切にせよと みんな言う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:43.04,default,,0,0,0,,That's why everybody tells\Nyou to treasure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:46.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親も教師も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.77,default,,0,0,0,,Your parents and teachers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:50.41,default,,0,0,0,,The commentators who\Nappear on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,テレビに出てくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見識者とかいう やから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.30,default,,0,0,0,,Even the musicians say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:54.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,果ては ミュージシャンまでもが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:54.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:57.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命は大切にせよとのう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.42,default,,0,0,0,,You should cherish\Nyour life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.65,default,,0,0,0,,That's why you shouldn't\Nfollow their advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:04.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 駄目なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:09.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命は もっと粗末に扱うべきなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:09.29,default,,0,0,0,,Your life should be\Nthrown around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:14.98,default,,0,0,0,,It'll stagnate and rot if\Nyou over protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命というやつは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,丁寧に扱い過ぎると
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:15.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よどみ 腐る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:20.14,default,,0,0,0,,People nowadays care about\Nthemselves too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:20.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近のやからは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:20.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 己を大事にしすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:24.98,default,,0,0,0,,As a result, they can't grasp\Nany opportunities,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:25.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果 チャンスをつかむこともなく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.98,default,,0,0,0,,and end up rotting away\Njust like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ズルズルと腐ってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:31.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その点 カイジ君は すばらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:31.18,default,,0,0,0,,In that respect,\NKaiji is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:35.04,default,,0,0,0,,He's someone that I\Nlook upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが見込んだ男じゃ やはり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:39.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命の使いどころというものを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:39.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心得ておる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:39.14,default,,0,0,0,,He understands how to\Nmake use of his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.86,default,,0,0,0,,Just as you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさしく 君の言うとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:49.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は つかむか死ぬかのときなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:48.63,default,,0,0,0,,it is now the time to grab\Nthe chance, or die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:53.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:53.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,めちゃくちゃだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.56,default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.20,default,,0,0,0,,This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雑魚には分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.68,default,,0,0,0,,Commoners like you\Nwon't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:04:00.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ生きたいだけの雑魚にはな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:04:00.31,default,,0,0,0,,You only care about\Nsurviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:06.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:06.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の生き死にの ばくち
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.14,default,,0,0,0,,I'll accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.18,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's life-or-death gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.31,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.06,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:24.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,払えよ 俺が勝ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:26.30,default,,0,0,0,,You'd better pay up!\NPay me the 9 million if I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっちり 900万
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 謝るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.71,default,,0,0,0,,Then you have to apologise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでいった仲間たちに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.94,default,,0,0,0,,Apologise to my dead comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:39.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川　お前が！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:39.29,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa, you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:51.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心したまえ　わしに二言はない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:51.43,default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry, I won't\Ngo back on my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:54.93,default,,0,0,0,,I will pay you the money\Nif you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:55.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が勝てば ちゃんと払う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.52,default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll make Tonegawa\Napologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:59.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 利根川に謝らせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:03.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土下座でも何でもさせてな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:03.07,default,,0,0,0,,I'll even make him\Nkneel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:09.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… おい そっちの準備もな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:09.50,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, go get the\Npreparations now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:10.98,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.67,default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:17.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:17.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心して挑みたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.69,default,,0,0,0,,Just relax and take up\Nthe challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:23.19,default,,0,0,0,,If you win, you'll get your\Nrevenge and 20 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:23.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば 無念を晴らし 2000万
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.02,default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ければ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.90,default,,0,0,0,,If you lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.23,default,,0,0,0,,You will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:38.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬ！ハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:43.37,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, clean that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:45.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 何か拭くものを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:44.13,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.25,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.72,default,,0,0,0,,Take off your watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時計を外せ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.35,default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep it for you until\Nthis battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負が終わるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,預かっておく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.14,default,,0,0,0,,Is a paper towel all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペーパータオルですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でもかまわん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.43,default,,0,0,0,,Anything will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.30,default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.43,default,,0,0,0,,You may begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,始めたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.43,default,,0,0,0,,The final E-Card battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:15.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｅカード 最終戦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生死を賭けたオーラスが始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:19.31,default,,0,0,0,,The life-or-death gamble has\Nfinally begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目は皇帝の利根川から
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.95,default,,0,0,0,,It begins with Tonegawa on\Nthe Emperor side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:28.45,default,,0,0,0,,This is the first game\Nthat he's serious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この最終戦 初めての真剣勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:32.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでの利根川は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:32.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕時計に仕組まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:35.03,default,,0,0,0,,Up to this point, he relied on\Nhis watch to play his card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,計器を頼りに カードを出してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負をするふりをしてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけである
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.24,default,,0,0,0,,He has been pretending\Nall this while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.36,default,,0,0,0,,However, this final battle\Nis different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:41.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし この最終戦は違う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼みの計器は ない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.38,default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have his\Ntrusted watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あくまで 己の読み 勘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.72,default,,0,0,0,,He has to rely on his\Nown judgement,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 運で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝利をもぎ取るしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.21,default,,0,0,0,,intuition, and luck to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:54.04,default,,0,0,0,,It's a life-or-death match with\Nno room for mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:54.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まごうことなき 真剣勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.95,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa has an overwhelming\Nadvantage as the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:58.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝側である利根川は 圧倒的有利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.95,default,,0,0,0,,However, he can't afford to\Nlose at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:01.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 逆に言えば負けられない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:04.31,default,,0,0,0,,If he loses the game,\Nit won't be an easy escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ければ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただではすまないということ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは誰よりも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川自身が分かっている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:10.46,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa is more aware of that\Nthan anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けられない…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:13.96,default,,0,0,0,,I cannot lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.84,default,,0,0,0,,I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ　それしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:21.69,default,,0,0,0,,I have overcome various\Ndifficulties so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:22.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは今まで幾多の苦境を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:22.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つことによって越えてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.71,default,,0,0,0,,I just need to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:25.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てばいいだけのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:30.21,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[Slave]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで 先ほどの不覚も埋め合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.69,default,,0,0,0,,That will make up for my\Nearlier failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:30.21,default,,0,0,0,,and let me regain\Nthe director's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長の信頼も回復できる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:31.62,default,,0,0,0,,I must win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:36.49,default,,0,0,0,,I will win...\Nand kill this brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:36.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝って この餓鬼を殺し…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.20,default,,0,0,0,,I will survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残るのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.47,default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:46.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この わしが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:53.14,default,,0,0,0,,If I'm able to gauge when his\Nemotions are shaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:53.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,慎重に やつの感情のブレ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.87,default,,0,0,0,,I can win the game easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:57.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,濃い薄いを計れば勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:01.64,default,,0,0,0,,I can use the Emperor for the\Nsecond or third rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:02.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後出しの２枚目か４枚目に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:02.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負を賭けて皇帝を出すか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民を出し続け
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.17,default,,0,0,0,,Or I can continue with\NCitizen cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:07.78,default,,0,0,0,,and let him destroy himself\Nwith his Slave card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手が奴隷カードを出して
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自滅するのを待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.21,default,,0,0,0,,That should be the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが常法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も１枚目で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負に行くことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:13.38,default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to end the battle\Nwith the first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.90,default,,0,0,0,,No, in that case I should go\Nwith the first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:22.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや だからこそ逆に１枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.27,default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit him on his blind spot\Nwhile he's unaware!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常法の裏をかき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,盲点をついた不意打ち
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.96,default,,0,0,0,,I should play it as\Nthe first card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.47,default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:37.11,default,,0,0,0,,If he used the Emperor card,\Nthis bet would be much easier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:37.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで 皇帝を出せたら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:37.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どれほど ばくちは楽か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや そう単純ではないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.94,default,,0,0,0,,No! It's not so simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:49.38,default,,0,0,0,,What if he read my intention of\Nlaunching a surprise attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:49.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし 今わしが考えた不意打ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:49.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつに読まれたとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:00.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆をついて やつは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:00.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷を出してくるかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:09:00.20,default,,0,0,0,,He might counter that by\Nusing the Slave card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつまで時間をかけるつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.09,default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:05.47,default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going\Nto drag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビクビク ノロノロと…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:07.47,default,,0,0,0,,You're so slow and timid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:11.21,default,,0,0,0,,That's why the old man has\Ngiven up on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:11.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなざまだから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:11.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長のじじいに見限られる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.21,default,,0,0,0,,You're merely someone\Nwho waits for instructions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:15.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,指示待ち人間なんて言われるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:15.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぬう…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ こいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.77,default,,0,0,0,,T-This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.73,default,,0,0,0,,This brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:27.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この餓鬼が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.73,default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺す　殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっ殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:32.09,default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:39.97,default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:42.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:41.80,default,,0,0,0,,I must calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これこそ やつの手かもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.48,default,,0,0,0,,This might be part of his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.74,default,,0,0,0,,It's his plan to make me\Ngo for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:50.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あおって わしに勝負をさせる腹…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:50.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,挑発に乗るのは危険だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.30,default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't fall into\Nhis trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:55.35,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa finally plays his\Nfirst card!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:56.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 ようやく１枚目を提出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:59.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受けて カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:59.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,即座に１枚目を提出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:59.86,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji responds immediately with\Nhis first card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,両者オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.55,default,,0,0,0,,Both sides open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.13,default,,0,0,0,,Citizen against Citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:09.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民と市民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:12.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 一歩 利根川を追い詰める
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:12.37,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji closes the gap with\NTonegawa by one step!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.03,default,,0,0,0,,Another step into\Nthe abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奈落へと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出せないだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むう…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.38,default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't use it here,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:23.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ 分かっていても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:26.08,default,,0,0,0,,You just couldn't use the\NEmperor as your first card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:26.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか１枚目に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:26.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝は出せやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:29.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝は有利だっていう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:29.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余裕があるうちは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:29.62,default,,0,0,0,,Although the Emperor has\Nthe advantage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:34.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろいろ考えたあげく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:34.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 保険を打ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:33.59,default,,0,0,0,,you'd go for the safer option\Nafter some consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は まだまだ様子を見てるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むう…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.48,default,,0,0,0,,You're just watching\Nand waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:42.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,びびりながらな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.80,default,,0,0,0,,...while quaking in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.80,default,,0,0,0,,So all I have to do\Nis to move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その点 俺は ただ行くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:50.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？こ こいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.31,default,,0,0,0,,T-This fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:54.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごみの分際で開き直りおって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.70,default,,0,0,0,,This piece of trash\Nis being defiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:58.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失うもののない くずは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:58.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうやって すぐ開き直る
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.93,default,,0,0,0,,People like him with\Nnothing to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.92,default,,0,0,0,,...tend to be defiant\Nvery quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが わしは違う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.14,default,,0,0,0,,However, I am different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:05.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のようなカスと違って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:05.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,積み上げてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:05.09,default,,0,0,0,,Compared to you trash,\NI have made my way up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何十年と
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.25,default,,0,0,0,,...for decades!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:12.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命知らずに負けて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:12.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えるわけには いかんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.59,default,,0,0,0,,I can't be reckless and \Nlet it all disappear before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝たなければ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.05,default,,0,0,0,,I have to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.60,default,,0,0,0,,I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.60,default,,0,0,0,,I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝たなければ… ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.61,default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:41.06,default,,0,0,0,,That stain on the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのカードの汚れ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.66,default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:48.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのときの…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.66,default,,0,0,0,,It was from just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:55.30,default,,0,0,0,,That stain mark was\Nleft behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,拭いた跡… 拭き残しか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:58.92,default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:04.88,default,,0,0,0,,That means, the cards with\Nblood stains were...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:06.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:06.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき 血がかかったカードは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:09.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,11戦で使った２枚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:08.75,default,,0,0,0,,...the two cards used\Nin the 11th round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使わなかった３枚は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:14.21,default,,0,0,0,,The three unused cards\Nwere left on his lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:16.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,既に やつの膝の上に置かれていて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:16.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血は かからなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.26,default,,0,0,0,,so they weren't stained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:17.97,default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり あのカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,11戦で使われた市民か奴隷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:21.55,default,,0,0,0,,those cards were used in the\N11th round.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:24.00,default,,0,0,0,,The Citizen and the Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２分の１の確率で
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷ということだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:28.28,default,,0,0,0,,There is a 50% chance that\None of them is the Slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:29.94,default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:31.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しめた　思わぬ隙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:32.24,default,,0,0,0,,It's an unexpected opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:37.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 当然 市民を選択
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:37.08,default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Tonegawa uses\Nthe Citizen card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.19,default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い 奴隷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.51,default,,0,0,0,,They opened the cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:46.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 市民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:44.32,default,,0,0,0,,But, it's a Citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目も引き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.32,default,,0,0,0,,The 2nd round is also\Na draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.35,default,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次に 汚れの付いたカードが来たら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:56.75,default,,0,0,0,,When the next stained card\Ncomes along,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必然的に残った１枚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.03,default,,0,0,0,,it'll be the remaining one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.00,default,,0,0,0,,The Slave card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:05.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 奴隷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:09.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… 奴隷なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:08.35,default,,0,0,0,,It's the Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.58,default,,0,0,0,,I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:13.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる　勝てるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.22,default,,0,0,0,,I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:14.65,default,,0,0,0,,I can survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:19.58,default,,0,0,0,,If I wait for him to play the\Nstained card,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血の付いたカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出るのを待って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:22.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この市民を出せば…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:22.99,default,,0,0,0,,then use my Citizen card...\NI can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる　勝って生き残る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:24.78,default,,0,0,0,,I can win and survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.63,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:32.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て　よく考えてみれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.15,default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら市民のカードに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血痕が残っていたとはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.74,default,,0,0,0,,even though the Citizen card \Nhad a stain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:38.34,default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean that the\NSlave card was stained as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:39.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷にも付いているとは限らない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:43.68,default,,0,0,0,,The stain on the Citizen card\Nwas left after wiping, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:44.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民カードに残った血は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:44.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あくまで拭き残し
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.97,default,,0,0,0,,The blood on the Slave card may\Nhave been wiped off completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷カードの血は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きれいに拭き取られたかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.72,default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:52.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばかが　何を浮かれている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.76,default,,0,0,0,,Why am I so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確証などない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.78,default,,0,0,0,,I can't be sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血痕が残っているか どうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:59.97,default,,0,0,0,,He can't be sure that the\Nother card was stained as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:14:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その両方の可能性を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:14:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捨てきることはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:02.90,default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:03.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのことが 利根川をためらわせた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:07.46,default,,0,0,0,,For the third round, Tonegawa from\Nthe Emperor side plays first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:07.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３枚目 皇帝の利根川の先出し
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.21,default,,0,0,0,,There's no proof that the\Nstained card is the Slave card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷カードに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血痕が残っている確証はない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 同時に血痕が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残っていないとも言い切れない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:16.37,default,,0,0,0,,But, nobody can tell if there's\Nno stain on the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３枚目 勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.52,default,,0,0,0,,The cards are opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.89,default,,0,0,0,,Citizen and Citizen!\NIt's a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民と市民　引き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.39,default,,0,0,0,,This has happened three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:37.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みたび繰り返される均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.11,default,,0,0,0,,Before they knew it,\Nit's the 4th round...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:40.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気が付けば４枚目　すなわち…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:42.40,default,,0,0,0,,...which is the final round.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:42.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終選択
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:47.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヒヒ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:50.32,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's turn to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:51.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４枚目は カイジの先出し
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.32,default,,0,0,0,,It's a 50-50 chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確率50％
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:56.09,default,,0,0,0,,A choice between\Nlife-or-death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生死を分ける二者択一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.91,default,,0,0,0,,Heaven or hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天国か地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:03.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生還か破滅かを決す 最終選択
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:02.36,default,,0,0,0,,A final choice to determine\Nsurvival or destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.69,default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:10.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.66,default,,0,0,0,,It's okay even if\NI die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:13.16,default,,0,0,0,,I must put myself aside and\Njust go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分を捨て 行け
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:16.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運命の１枚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:16.16,default,,0,0,0,,This is the card of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.10,default,,0,0,0,,There's no blood stain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:34.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ない　血痕が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:38.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり 拭き取られてしまったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:37.18,default,,0,0,0,,As expected, the stain was\Nwiped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも 残りの１枚が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.55,default,,0,0,0,,Or could it be the\Nlast card?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおっ 来た　血痕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.84,default,,0,0,0,,There it is, the blood stain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.00,default,,0,0,0,,It's the Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:16:01.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ… 勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:00.31,default,,0,0,0,,I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.48,default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill the Slave with\Nmy Citizen and win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:05.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この市民で 奴隷を殺して勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:11.82,default,,0,0,0,,You'll die soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:12.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬ お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:18.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耳をそぎ落とした その気迫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:18.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その胆力は すさまじかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:19.19,default,,0,0,0,,Your courage in sacrificing\Nyour ear was fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,褒めてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.33,default,,0,0,0,,I commend you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:24.90,default,,0,0,0,,But you brought this\Nmassive bleeding upon yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:26.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 結局は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:26.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その大量出血が あだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:28.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,墓穴を掘ることになったな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.83,default,,0,0,0,,You dug your own grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.08,default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:49.09,default,,0,0,0,,Just as he laid down his card,\Ndoubt entered his mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:49.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを提出する直前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:49.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川の脳裏に浮かんだ疑念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:53.82,default,,0,0,0,,He doubted that Kaiji\Nwould overlook this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:53.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,果たして カイジは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:53.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気付かないだろうか？という疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:58.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自ら相手に手の内を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:58.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知られるような致命的ミス
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:58.41,default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't make the mistake\Nof revealing his card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:04.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この血痕に カイジが気付かない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:04.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことが あり得るだろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:03.84,default,,0,0,0,,He doubted that Kaiji would\Nnot notice the blood stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ましてや この血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ自身が まき散らし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.61,default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, Kaiji was the one\Nwho bled on the cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分で拭き取ったもの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.50,default,,0,0,0,,...before wiping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:13.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 拭き残しという可能性も
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:13.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,承知しているはず
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:13.49,default,,0,0,0,,Of course he knew it's possible to\Nleave stains on his cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:17.35,default,,0,0,0,,How could he simply\Nleave stains like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:18.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その上で 残った血痕を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:18.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見逃しているというのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:21.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありえん　こいつほどの男は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:19.50,default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.72,default,,0,0,0,,For a man like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら耳を切り落とした激痛を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伴っているとはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:25.35,default,,0,0,0,,no matter how much pain he's\Nsuffering from losing his ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:28.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見過ごすなど考えられん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.36,default,,0,0,0,,he wouldn't have\Noverlooked this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:31.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負 やつにとっては
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:31.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遊びではない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:31.76,default,,0,0,0,,This match isn't just\Na game to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:35.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命懸け　負ければ死が待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:34.86,default,,0,0,0,,He bet his life on it.\NHe will die if he loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血の拭き残しなど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:39.87,default,,0,0,0,,He'd have obsessively checked\Nfor any blood stains left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:40.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:40.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神経質にチェックするはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対にありえんミスだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.87,default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't make\Nsuch a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ… ざわざわざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:52.73,default,,0,0,0,,With that in mind, he might\Nuse the stained cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう考えると
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血痕の付いたカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:56.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが後出しの２枚目 ４枚目で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:56.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てくるというのも出来すぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.52,default,,0,0,0,,...for the second\Nand fourth rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:03.02,default,,0,0,0,,It's strange enough that he\Nbet 18 mm in this final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも この最終戦に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:04.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,18ミリ勝負を挑むということ自体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:04.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異常な決断
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:03.02,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[Slave, Emperor]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷での勝負で何の勝算もなく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:07.17,default,,0,0,0,,There's no chance of\Nwinning with the Slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気じみた勝負に出るはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.63,default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't attempt\Nsomething so absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,盛ったな？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.00,default,,0,0,0,,You've poisoned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:18.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負に毒を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.27,default,,0,0,0,,You've poisoned this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:21.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いなく わなを仕掛けた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.92,default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that\Nhe laid a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この餓鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:23.18,default,,0,0,0,,This brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:27.25,default,,0,0,0,,He has a plan, and he's just\Nwaiting for the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か策を打ち その上で待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:30.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの失策　うかつな決断を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:31.25,default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for me to make a\Nmistake, a careless decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:41.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… 見かけによらず この男
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:43.46,default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of his appearance,\Nthis man is a deceitful snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:44.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人をだまし食らう蛇よ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つためには手段を選ばぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,卑劣な やから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:47.54,default,,0,0,0,,He would do anything to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:54.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ものを言わず近づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:54.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,背後から刺す非道 冷血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:51.88,default,,0,0,0,,He'd silently stab someone\Nin the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.40,default,,0,0,0,,He's cold-blooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:58.42,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he left\Nthose blood stains on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの血痕は故意に残したもの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.45,default,,0,0,0,,That's his strategy, his trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつの戦略 わな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:06.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血を拭き取った後に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:06.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,改めて付けた目くらましか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.45,default,,0,0,0,,It's a diversion he used\Nafter wiping off the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや あくまで血は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:10.96,default,,0,0,0,,No, he had to make it look\Nlike the stains still remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:12.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,拭き残したように
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:12.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見せなければならん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:16.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,片手しか自由の利かぬやつが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:16.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下手に小細工の動きをすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:16.91,default,,0,0,0,,With only one free hand,\Nif he had tried any small move,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.96,default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have let it slip by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:19.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが見逃すわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:22.60,default,,0,0,0,,So, it was leftover from\Nthe last time after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり あのときの拭き残し
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:33.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　あのとき 既に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:33.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードが すり替わっていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:29.31,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:32.61,default,,0,0,0,,He had already\Nswapped the cards then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:37.12,default,,0,0,0,,While I was distracted with\Ntalking to the director,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:38.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが会長の話に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:38.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気を取られている隙に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:42.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつは 手の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:42.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民カードを仕込み…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:41.38,default,,0,0,0,,he took the Citizen card\Nthat was in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.82,default,,0,0,0,,Then swapped it with the\NSlave card on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,テーブルの上の
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷カードと すり替えた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出血は その後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.36,default,,0,0,0,,He splattered the blood\Nafter that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき 血が付いたカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民と奴隷ではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:55.79,default,,0,0,0,,At that time, the stained cards\Nweren't Citizen and Slave,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:58.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚とも市民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.37,default,,0,0,0,,but both Citizen cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.49,default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:03.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:03.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな とんでもないトリックを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.87,default,,0,0,0,,He used such an\Nincredible trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この土壇場で ぬけぬけと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:05.40,default,,0,0,0,,He's so impudent even\Nin these last moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.53,default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:12.34,default,,0,0,0,,This is possible for someone who\Nsurvived the Espoir and the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:12.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがは エスポワールや橋で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:12.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残っただけのことはある
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つわものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.12,default,,0,0,0,,He's a veteran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 残念ながら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:20.12,default,,0,0,0,,However, it's too bad that you\Nwon't be able to outwit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしには
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一歩 届かなかったようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヒヒ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:32.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… 惜しいな カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.20,default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の盛った毒は漏れたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.74,default,,0,0,0,,The poison you put in\Nhas leaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:41.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか見事な盛り方だったが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.64,default,,0,0,0,,It was quite a smart way\Nof poisoning though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:46.12,default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't work on me\Nwho avoid to swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:43.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,服毒には至らず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:47.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは回避した
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:50.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね　蛇が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:49.92,default,,0,0,0,,Die, you snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:53.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが とどめ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.62,default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:56.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を殺す 鉄ついだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:56.71,default,,0,0,0,,This is the iron hammer\Nthat will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヒヒ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:15.10,default,,0,0,0,,The final judgement has\Nfinally been given.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに下される最終審判
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの前に開かれる扉は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生か？死か？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:18.32,default,,0,0,0,,Will the door that is\Nopened for Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.35,default,,0,0,0,,...be the door of life,\Nor death?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:45.96,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Enforcement.
